>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A screensaver inspired by Apple's Event on October 30, 2018</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/pedrommcarrasco/Brooklyn#readme\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/brooklyn.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n<p>Free</p>","updatedAt":"2019-03-15T17:31:00.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>MusaicFM</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>October 30</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Smoothly changes between 371 Apple logos from their 2018 iPad event.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Free</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/lekevicius/october30\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/october30.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2019-03-15T17:31:00.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>ScreenMazer</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Continuously builds and then solves a maze, while displaying the current time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/dado3212/screenmazer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/screenMazer.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2019-03-04T19:30:25.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>ColorClock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Displays a solid color corresponding to the current time.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/edwardloveall/colorclocksaver\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/colorClockSaver.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2018-08-13T15:44:53.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Simple Clock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A simple clock screensaver with different analogue clock faces as skins.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Free</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Wandmalfarbe/Simple-Clock-Screensaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/simpleClock.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2018-08-10T14:37:07.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Word Clock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A super simple word clock, like your computer is typing the time for you.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/chrstphrknwtn/word-clock-screensaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/wordClock2.gif\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2018-03-12T19:47:30.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Graphics</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Emoji Saver</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Animates Apple, EmojiOne and Twitter Emojis in 7 different effects with many customizable settings.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Lite Version (Free) and Full Version ($3)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.emojisaver.eu/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/emojiSaver.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2017-06-09T19:23:48.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Developer</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>MacOS Kernel Panic</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Harmless screensaver that faithfully emulates the horrifying experience of a kernel panic.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Free</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://doomlaser.com/kernel-panic-screensaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/macosKernelPanic.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2017-04-06T09:00:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Developer</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Windows Kernel Panic</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Blue Screen of Death (BSOD) screensaver for Mac.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Free</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/dessibelle/Blue-Screen-Saver\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/kernelPanic.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2017-01-23T08:16:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Epoch Flip Clock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Unix Time (epoch) flip clock.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/chrstphrknwtn/epoch-flip-clock-screensaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/epochFlipClock.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-11-20T13:12:12.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Grid Clock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Twelve hour time in words.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/chrstphrknwtn/grid-clock-screensaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/gridClock.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-11-20T13:11:07.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Retro</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>PongSaver</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>PongSaver is an macOS screensaver/clock which keeps time by using the score of a game of Pong. The left side wins once an hour, and the right side wins once a minute.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://mikeash.com/software/pongsaver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/pongSaver.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T14:24:41.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Developer</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Developer Excuses</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A macOS Screensaver which shows quotes from <a href=\"http://developerexcuses.com\">http://developerexcuses.com</a> (unofficial).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/kimar/DeveloperExcuses\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/developerExcuses.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-09-22T14:24:41.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Other</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Google Trends</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Shows the latest hot searches for all regions or specific countries.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Free</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.google.com/trends/hottrends/visualize?nrow=5&#x26;ncol=5\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/googleTrends.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-08-25T15:48:27.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Today</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Time or date displayed in a similar way to On Kawara's \"Today Series\" paintings.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.gingerbeardman.com/today/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/today.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-04-08T22:16:44.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Fractal Clock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A clock that produces a fractal tree pattern around it as it moves.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dqd.com/~mayoff/programs/FractalClock/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/fractalClock.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2016-03-16T04:04:03.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Graphics</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Screensson</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Creates unique patterns on your display by randomly stacking vector stencils.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Donationware</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.siggieggertsson.com/Saver-Screensson\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/screensson.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T22:44:39.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>fliqlo</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A flip clock screensaver.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://fliqlo.com/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/fliqlo.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Clocks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Word Clock</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A clock made of words. It switches between a circular and a paragraph layout.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.simonheys.com/wordclock/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/wordClock.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Apple Inspired</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Aerial</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Apple TV Aerial Screensaver for Mac.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/JohnCoates/Aerial\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/aerial.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Apple Inspired</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Apple Watch</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A screensaver that looks like an Apple Watch.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rasmusnielsen.dk/applewatch/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/appleWatch.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>MusaicFM</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>iOS Lockscreen for macOS</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A screensaver that looks like the lockscreen on iPhone and iPad.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://littleendiangamestudios.com/project/ios-8-screen-saver/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/iOSLockscreen.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Retro</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Textify Me</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This interactive screen saver turns everything in front of your camera into text.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>$0.99</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/textify-me/id470453599\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/textifyMe.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Sci-Fi</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>The Github Matrix Screensaver</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The latest commits from GitHub visualized in a Matrix-style animation.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/winterbe/github-matrix-screensaver\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/githubMatrix.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Sci-Fi</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>StarWarsScroll</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Recreates the opening titles of the first 6 Star Wars movies.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://download.cnet.com/StarWarsScroll-Screen-Saver/3000-2257_4-82580.html\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/starWarsScroll.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Video Game</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>SpeedS@ver</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Plays videos of people completing speed runs of games.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/orta/SpeedS-ver\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/speedS@ver.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Aquarium</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Aquarium live lite</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Video of aquariums.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/aquarium-live-lite-relaxing/id462563503\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/aquariumLive.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Graphics</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3>Electric Sheep Infinite Evolving Artwork</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Animations of evolving fractals.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Free</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://electricsheep.org/\"><img src=\"https://github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers/raw/master/screenshots/electricSheep.png\" alt=\"\"></a></p>","updatedAt":"2015-11-12T16:22:21.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/AppImageCommunity/awesome-appimage","repo":"AppImageCommunity/awesome-appimage"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/jaywcjlove/awesome-mac","repo":"jaywcjlove/awesome-mac"}},"pageContext":{"type":"week","repo":"agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers","id":"awesomes/github.com/agarrharr/awesome-macos-screensavers","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/AppImageCommunity/awesome-appimage","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/jaywcjlove/awesome-mac"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","282